16 of Two Hundred Dollars ($200.00) to be deposited
17 into the Trauma Care Assistance Revolving Fund
18 created in Section 1-2530.9 of Title 63 of the
19 Oklahoma Statutes, for each suspension or
20 revocation as shown by the records of Service
